#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig2.7:3.1"
msgid "7. Mittātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "thig2.7:4.1"
msgid "<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^vv15#6 [Uttarāvimānavatthu] | ^ja489#14 [Surucijātaka]\" id=\"note20\">*</span> <a class=\"sc\" id=\"1\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id=\"verse-num-sc31\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts31\"></a>“Cātuddasiṃ pañcadasiṃ,"
msgstr "On the fourteenth day,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:4.2"
msgid "yā ca pakkhassa aṭṭhamī;"
msgstr "the fifteenth and the eighth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:4.3"
msgid "Pāṭihāriyapakkhañca,"
msgstr "as well as during the fortnight of special displays"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:4.4"
msgid "aṭṭhaṅgasusamāgataṃ."
msgstr "I kept the sabbath, "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc32"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts32"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts127"></a>
msgctxt "thig2.7:5.1"
msgid "Uposathaṃ upāgacchiṃ,"
msgstr "associated with the eight precepts"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:5.2"
msgid "devakāyābhinandinī;"
msgstr "I rejoiced at [rebirth] in a group of devas"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:5.3"
msgid "Sājja ekena bhattena,"
msgstr "Eating [once] a day"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:5.4"
msgid "muṇḍā saṅghāṭipārutā;"
msgstr "With shaven head, wearing the outer robe "

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:5.5"
msgid "Devakāyaṃ na patthehaṃ,"
msgstr "I don’t long for [rebirth] in a group of devas"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.7:5.6"
msgid "vineyya hadaye daran”ti."
msgstr "I’ve removed pain from my heart"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="3"></a>
